body.description: Looking for both OSHA and ANSI Compliance? We took our best value in a Class B ANSI standard and OSHA required content, added a pocket liner for your own customized content in the door space and ended up with this great 3-shelf, 1,382-piece industrial first aid station designed for smaller businesses, offices and work sites that may have machinery and other hazards which require a broader range and quantity of supplies to deal with injuries more complex or high-risk environments. Kit Includes: * (1) First Aid Booklet, 52 page * (1) Tri-Cut Adhesive Tape * (50) Antiseptic Wipes * (1) Tweezers * (40) Woven Knuckle Bandages * (40) Woven Fingertip Bandages * (1) Blood Stopper Bandage * (1) Eye Wash, 4oz/120ml * (200) Plastic Bandage Strips, 1" X 3" * (125) Cherry Cough Drops * (250) Aspirin Tablets * (250) Antacid Tablets* (50) Woven Bandages, 1" X 3" * (2) Instant Ice Pack * (100) Alcohol Wipes * (25) Gauze Pads, 3" X 3" * (25) Gauze Pads, 2" X 2" * (6) Tongue Depressor * (8) Exam Gloves * (25) Triple Antibiotic Ointment .5gm * (2) Triangular Bandage * (2) Gauze Clean Wrap 2" X 4.1yd * (1) Gauze Clean Wrap 4" X 4.1yd * (1) Antiseptic Spray * (1) Burn Spray * (4) ABD Combine Pad, Sterile 5" X 9" * (1) Scissors 4.5" * (2) Burn Dressing, 4” X 4” * (1) Self-Adherent Wrap 3" X 5 yd * (1) CPR Mouth Barrier * (10) Hand Sanitizer .9gm * (1) Padded Aluminum Splint * (1) Tourniquet, 1" X 12" * (1) Easy Refill Checklist * (1) ANSI Class B Label * (1) Pocket Liner * (1) 3 Shelf First Aid Cabinet
